summary:
A Software Engineer who enjoys connecting the dots: be it ideas from different disciplines, people from different teams, or applications from different industries. I have strong technical skills and an academic background in engineering.

Today, I am studying Data Science as a master's student at Berliner Hochschule für Technik (BHT). Formerly, I worked as a Python Developer at Tata Consultancy Services (TCS), India, for 3 years and interned as a Unity Developer at a growing new-age company. I have also taken the initiative and explored my interests to constantly learn new things and play with different projects using different languages and tools.

Technical Skills:
- Languages: Python (Pandas, Numpy, MatPlotLib), SQL (MySQL, PostgreSQL), C#, DAX, HTML, CSS
- Tools/Technologies: Azure Databricks, Microsoft Power BI, Microsoft Excel, Git, Jira, Unity
- Industry Knowledge: Data Structures and Algorithms, Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA), Object-Oriented Programming

I enjoy exploring and connecting with people across a range of industries, so don't hesitate to reach out if you'd like to get in touch: mishrachiraag@gmail.com
